277
00:22:28,900 --> 00:22:30,580
For us,

278
00:22:33,220 --> 00:22:37,780
we're going to donate everything we wear right now.  Right, Seo Yeon?

279
00:22:39,140 --> 00:22:43,160
 The more expensive, the better.  The much, much, more expensive, the better.

280
00:22:44,920 --> 00:22:48,910
