310
00:25:55,860 --> 00:26:01,500
Since an heir of Shinhwa Food eats food with us, I'm so honored that I don't know what to do.

311
00:26:01,500 --> 00:26:07,890
I know, right?  Teacher Lee Min Hyeok, an heir of Shinhwa Food does it, right?

312
00:26:10,420 --> 00:26:14,090
Teacher Lee Min Hyeok, may I have a question?

313
00:26:14,090 --> 00:26:18,380
